items.name: OBJECTSPECIFIC
desc: This value specifies that the standard object projection method is used.

items.name: PARALLEL
desc: the 3D objects are drawn in the parallel projection.
This value specifies a flat parallel projection in the specified degree of freedom (X or Y).

items.name: SPHERE
desc: forces normals to think that the object is a sphere.
This value forces projection to wrapping in X and/or Y.
